title: 4 of the Best Street Food Finds in Delhi
description:
Join us for a vegetarian’s dream tour of Delhi. Make room for fruit chaat, frozen desserts, samosas of many persuasions and an omelet made of moong lentils. (Omnivores, you’ll like it, too.)

SUBSCRIBE: https://goo.gl/vR6Acb

#Delhi #India #Food 

This story is a part of our Flavors series, where we do so much more than play with our food. Come with us as we dive into deliciously different and tastefully off-beat stories in the culinary world.
